All Implemented Interfaces:

Direct Known Subclasses:
AllMatchesAgenda, ChangePropagationAgenda, ClosestLabelAgenda, CompleteAgenda, CompleteInstanceAgenda, EmptyAgenda, ExplicitAgenda, RandomAgenda
public class AgendaImpl
extends java.lang.Object
implements Agenda

The general implementation of an agenda. It handles all the calls for agendas. AgendaImpl itself does not create any AgendaElements itself they can only be added. AgendaElements have to be created in the extensions of Agenda.

Author:
Marc Ehrig
